<br>
We came across some tomes in Skyshrine a couple days ago and after much, much hunting and searching we have not come up with anything. The only Tome I have actually seen with my own eyes was Tome Of Elemental Mastery. No stats, no drop. The 2 others that were looted were Tome of Enlightenment (or Enlightened Thought don't remember which) and the third one I was not even there for so do not know it's name. My guildmates and I have roamed through Thurg, Kael, Iceclad, GD and EW trying to find any npc willing to give us the time of day to see what these tomes could possibly be for. Since they are no drop I can only assume they are part of a quest but we have found NO info anywhere. Hopefully someone can shed even a SMALL ray of sunshine here just to get us on the right foot. We have exhausted around 25-30 hours of just footing it from city to city to question every npc who would speak but still have no lead, no start and no info on these tomes. If anyone knows anything about these I'm not looking for the whole quest...just the START of the road. I enjoy the thrill of the hunt on quests but this one has me overly stumped. Thank you in advance.<br>
<br>
Thryven<br>
